<h3 id="lopezosa-carlos-codina-lluis-fern√°ndez-planells-ariadna-y-freixa-pere-2021-journalistic-innovation-how-new-formats-of-digital-journalism-are-perceived-in-the-academic-literaturejournalism">Lopezosa, Carlos, Codina, Lluis, Fern√°ndez-Planells, Ariadna y Freixa, Pere (2021). <a href="https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/full/10.1177/14648849211033434">Journalistic innovation: How new formats of digital journalism are perceived in the academic literature</a>.¬†<em>Journalism</em>.</h3>

